    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may grant a motif that allows the target to subsume themselves in the group. The target gains an aura with a radius of 30 feet that gives allies other than the target a +2 insight bonus to saving throws against mind-affecting effects. This bonus increases by +1 for every 5 caster levels.</p>\n<p>The target may discharge this effect when an ally within close range takes damage to shift up to half the damage the ally takes to themselves. The target may discharge this effect even if the damage their ally would take would normally reduce them below 1 hit point, and even if it would kill them outright. Damage is transferred after the effects of damage reduction, energy resistance, immunity and similar effects. The damage transferred is empathic in nature and cannot be further reduced, divided, or transferred.</p>\n",
